text: Bernried am Starnberger See is a municipality in Weilheim-Schongau in Bavaria, Germany. It is on the shore of Starnberger See. ==Gallery== Germany - Green farm Around Starnberger See - panoramio.jpg|Green farmland around Stamberger See ==References== Category:Weilheim-Schongau
